metadata.name: Ethical Ambitions
metadata.description:
This Artwork Depicts Different Stages of life when society Pressurize you about many irrelevant things. Woman Break the Chain and Heading Towards the Whale (which itself a Symbol of Hope), depicts that one should ignore all the Negative Thoughts in Life and Focus on Good Things. Only Hope can Lead us to a Good Consequence. Life is tough sometimes and all we can do is try to move forward. The point is not to lose hope in life.  
Resolution - 1700*2000

PERKS - 
Every Collector who bids on this will be eligible for free NFT AirDrop from this Collection. 
Note - Multiple Biddings wont make you eligible for Multiple AirDrops.
